instruction: Syndicate the financial information in the following article.
input: Walmart Inc has seen a surge in their profits from their online sales. It has been reported that the retail giant saw a 37% increase in its web sales in operations outside of China. This was an unexpected success compared to their usual growth rate of 20% to 25%.
output: Walmart Inc has experienced a surge in profits from its online sales, with a 37% increase in web sales in operations outside of China, exceeding their typical growth rate of 20-25%.
